14:44.736 --> 14:45.976
That's not okay with me.

14:45.977 --> 14:47.896
So we have got to control this conversation

14:47.897 --> 14:49.272
and put this to an end.

14:49.273 --> 14:51.543
All right, I understand that,
but I cannot do that, okay?

14:51.544 --> 14:52.695
Why not?

14:52.696 --> 14:54.799
I tell you what. You ask
good old Teddy, all right?

14:54.800 --> 14:57.095
- The hero.
- The pillar of society. Come on, now.

14:57.096 --> 14:59.627
Listen, I know it's not
easy for either one of you

14:59.628 --> 15:00.819
