to promote the hell out of it.

18:58.965 --> 19:01.269
Thank you. I really appreciate it.

19:05.061 --> 19:06.722
It was good to see you again.

19:08.410 --> 19:09.866
[Sighs]

19:13.695 --> 19:15.223
