that'd be really great.

19:16.315 --> 19:17.601
Rayna.

19:17.602 --> 19:19.674
I don't really care, because
all hell is breaking loose,

19:19.675 --> 19:20.898
and I guess the last person in the world

19:20.899 --> 19:23.756
you want talking to the press is
Deacon, after your shenanigans!

19:23.757 --> 19:26.379
It wasn't just me, okay? I
didn't force myself on Megan.

19:26.380 --> 19:28.539
- Ugh. Please.
- We were friends who got closer,

19:28.540 --> 19:31.316
and she was there for
me when nobody else was.

19:31.317 --> 19:34.121
Did you ever think about Maddie?
Or is that why you did it?

19:34.122 --> 19:35.657
'Cause Deacon's her father? Is that why?

19:35.658 --> 19:37.985
Oh... God!

19:37.986 --> 19:40.562
- I am so sick and tired of hearing that!
- Shh!

19:40.563 --> 19:41.611
I'm Maddie's father!

19:41.612 --> 19:42.923
I'm the one who's been there for her,

19:42.924 --> 19:45.740
and there's no way in hell that
I am just gonna step aside here!

19:45.741 --> 19:47.588
