19:55.700 --> 19:57.099
I'm the outsider!

19:57.100 --> 19:58.627
Let me tell you something right now.

19:58.628 --> 20:00.085
I am not losing Maddie.

20:00.564 --> 20:02.653
Not to him. Not to him.

