<i>Man: Rayna, is it true that you had
an affair with Deacon Claybourne?</i>

20:07.572 --> 20:09.075
<i>Did you know about this?</i>

20:09.076 --> 20:10.115
What?

20:10.116 --> 20:11.484
It's all over the news.

20:12.644 --> 20:13.963
<i>Rayna: Get your hands off her!</i>

20:13.964 --> 20:15.515
Oh, my God.

20:15.516 --> 20:17.067
<i>Stay the hell away from my kids!</i>

20:17.068 --> 20:19.559
Did you know that Deacon
had a daughter with Rayna?

20:19.560 --> 20:21.079
<i>Woman: Rayna! Rayna!</i>

20:21.080 --> 20:23.350
