And you didn't tell me.

20:24.087 --> 20:25.422
Say something.

20:26.151 --> 20:27.926
It wasn't my secret to tell.

20:28.612 --> 20:30.942
Betrayed by my own daughter,

20:31.278 --> 20:34.637
my own flesh and blood.

20:34.638 --> 20:35.509
Mama.

20:35.510 --> 20:36.493
I mean, Deacon's one thing

20:36.494 --> 20:39.685
because Rayna's always had him
wrapped around her little finger,

20:39.686 --> 20:41.221
- but you...
- I'm sorry.

20:41.222 --> 20:43.659
